Resource Profile: Immunization Immunization

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/ImmunizationImmunization Version: 1.5.11
Active as of 2025-05-08 Computable Name: ImmunizationImmunization

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file V IMMUNIZATION (9000010.11) to us-core-immunization.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: AMPL GUI and Lighthouse Patient Health API
  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
